KitKat::

She turned and looked at Blackfang. "Unicron? So what's one bot got 
to do with anything? Geesh, you sleep for what seems to an eon and 
you miss everything. OK, brief me on the latest scorecard on who's 
who and what's what."  She tilted her head to the side only a 
fraction and thought. She looked at Blackfang. "Uhm, please."
